Definitely one of my favourite postprocessing effects is Screen Space Reflections
Finally got around to implementing it in #threejs using @ImanolFotia's tutorial + code
For smooth reflections I blur the reflections and blend them with them clear ones depending on the ray distance https://t.co/uqm1iGjgGy

I've improved performances by calculating the point lights only in their area of influence.

You can test it live 👉 https://t.co/gtsl8gIGXM

Potential next steps: 
- Ambient Occlusion
- Reflection
- Antialias
